so that we can maintain relationship with

00:08:43.013 --> 00:08:47.303
what really is going on in truth and in reality here.

00:08:47.299 --> 00:08:49.799
This is first part of the check list.

00:08:49.799 --> 00:08:52.719
Second part of the check list is that, what is really

00:08:52.711 --> 00:08:59.169
going on here is that, it is a ceremony for us,

00:08:59.172 --> 00:09:03.309
not for Shri Mataji.  It is for us. We are benefitting

00:09:03.315 --> 00:09:05.815
from the Puja, not Shri Mataji.

00:09:05.815 --> 00:09:09.435
Why? Becasue Shri Mataji is on the tenth floor.

00:09:09.423 --> 00:09:11.165
We are on the first floor.

00:09:11.166 --> 00:09:14.055
When Shri Mataji is
Mahamaya, when She talks

00:09:14.064 --> 00:09:16.564
in a Public Programme,
when She speaks to us

00:09:16.569 --> 00:09:18.314
as a normal human being,

00:09:18.314 --> 00:09:19.934
She climbed down from the tenth floor

00:09:19.934 --> 00:09:22.434
and She looked very human, one of us

00:09:22.434 --> 00:09:24.934
and this is not so. She is not one of us, in that

00:09:24.934 --> 00:09:27.824
sense. Although She is
much more human than

00:09:27.824 --> 00:09:29.174
all of us put together.

00:09:29.190 --> 00:09:31.690
In truth She is not a Human Being. All right?

00:09:31.690 --> 00:09:35.964
Now,

00:09:35.974 --> 00:09:40.190
What happened is... in a
Puja we address ourselves

00:09:40.210 --> 00:09:42.961
to Shri Mataji in the
dimension where She is on

00:09:42.970 --> 00:09:45.231
the tenth floor.

00:09:45.231 --> 00:09:48.501
We address ourselves
to Her for what She is

00:09:48.497 --> 00:09:53.271
which is...The Infinite One

00:09:53.271 --> 00:09:58.606
and through this, the frequency of Shri Mataji's

00:09:58.626 --> 00:10:01.320
Chakras, which are addressed
in the proper protocol

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:09.391
start revolving... start
revolving at a much more

00:10:09.392 --> 00:10:11.511
subtle and higher frequency.

00:10:11.517 --> 00:10:15.167
In such a way, we can
absorb within three of four

00:10:15.162 --> 00:10:19.122
hours of Puja, what we cannot achieve

00:10:19.129 --> 00:10:22.122
within one or two years, perhaps, of meditation

00:10:22.135 --> 00:10:26.042
at home. This is the
perception we have to have

00:10:26.045 --> 00:10:29.616
before Puja, that we are here to benefit.

00:10:29.646 --> 00:10:31.652
It is for us.

00:10:31.652 --> 00:10:33.912
Because we enter in a relationship with Her

00:10:33.912 --> 00:10:38.582
in Her Truth, which is that She is the Goddess.

00:10:38.583 --> 00:10:41.083
Even if we don't know
it, even if we doubt it,

00:10:41.083 --> 00:10:46.213
even if we have questions
about it, this is our problem.

00:10:46.235 --> 00:10:49.923
The grass is green outside,
whether you like it or not

00:10:49.923 --> 00:10:52.125
and whether you are doubting or not.

00:10:52.125 --> 00:10:54.593
If you see the grass red, it's your problem.

00:10:54.575 --> 00:10:57.943
In the same way Shri Mataji is Adi Shakti.

00:10:57.973 --> 00:11:01.503
She is The Holy Spirit. She is the Primoridal Being

00:11:01.487 --> 00:11:07.313
and those who have not realised it
and there are many of us who have not,

00:11:07.323 --> 00:11:11.893
because it is a sacred privilege
to enter into that mystery.

00:11:11.883 --> 00:11:18.153
Next, with a desire to progress on the discovery
of the true nature of who Shri Mataji is.

00:11:18.151 --> 00:11:22.205
OK?  Puja is just for this.

00:11:22.205 --> 00:11:27.751
That was the second point that we are here
to benefit and what was the third point?

00:11:27.740 --> 00:11:32.190
Now let's see if anyone has listened to me here.

00:11:36.143 --> 00:11:38.643
I shouldn't forget it!  I'm sorry!

00:11:41.446 --> 00:11:45.962
OK. The third point is humility.

00:11:45.975 --> 00:11:48.475
You see,

00:11:50.646 --> 00:11:55.972
I remember one line, which was
written in this book and this is that

00:11:55.976 --> 00:12:02.746
humility is the security
of those who come near God,

00:12:02.742 --> 00:12:06.076
because God is something just... it's too much

00:12:06.095 --> 00:12:08.456
I mean, just way out

00:12:08.456 --> 00:12:12.666
There is no way, we can start
grasping what that Being

00:12:12.684 --> 00:12:17.456
is; even if it sitting before us in this little chair.

00:12:17.456 --> 00:12:21.292
So, we come with all kind of stuff within us,

00:12:21.300 --> 00:12:24.622
which is perhaps nice, and
perhaps also not so nice.

00:12:24.626 --> 00:12:34.928
The only way, we can come nearer to this
fantastic reality is to be humble;

00:12:34.958 --> 00:12:42.093
or else happens... what
has happened to many of us.

00:12:42.115 --> 00:12:45.303
is that we have to learn it the hard way.

00:12:45.333 --> 00:12:59.653
We are whirled around in various
paths of tests and tensions for us to discover

00:12:59.651 --> 00:13:06.913
that our ego is the one
who keeps us out of reality.

00:13:06.912 --> 00:13:14.430
Now we all have desires here. Right?  One is the desire to improve his health. OK

00:13:14.437 --> 00:13:17.057
Another one is the desire to get a job.

00:13:17.049 --> 00:13:24.047
The third one is the desire that
his wife should be all right.

00:13:24.047 --> 00:13:26.732
The third one, the fourth
one, the fifth one! OK?

00:13:26.732 --> 00:13:29.392
Everybody has a problem here alright.

00:13:29.392 --> 00:13:37.342
Now please put this shopping
bag of demands on the side

00:13:37.353 --> 00:13:43.278
and have only one desire, is
to be one with The Supreme,

00:13:43.298 --> 00:13:46.098
to be one with the reality

00:13:46.128 --> 00:13:50.108
to be one with God, because
that is what your Kundalini is,

00:13:50.107 --> 00:13:53.604
the desire to be one with God.

00:13:53.607 --> 00:14:01.466
And by asking for this, ask for the supreme.
The other things will be given 'en passant.'

00:14:01.466 --> 00:14:08.204
Don't ask for small stuff, because
you are facing a big giver

00:14:08.224 --> 00:14:11.978
and don't come in front of someone, who
has one billion dollars in the pocket

00:14:11.978 --> 00:14:13.947
asking for 5 dollars.

00:14:13.995 --> 00:14:18.808
Don't! It's stupid. It's not as
a Swiss that I'm speaking to you.

00:14:18.810 --> 00:14:22.400
It's a Sahaja Yogi; although
there is some element

00:14:22.400 --> 00:14:26.124
of Swiss consciousness
in this , I suppose.

00:14:27.729 --> 00:14:34.431
Be clever! You are in front of the biggest
giver of the world and don't ask for peanuts.

00:14:39.504 --> 00:14:41.534
It is true.  She is that

00:14:41.551 --> 00:14:45.948
If you would know, you would be
floating one metre above ground.

00:14:45.952 --> 00:14:49.328
I see some of you sitting
there, you just don't know it.

00:14:49.342 --> 00:14:53.658
So ask, "Mother may I know Who You are?"

00:14:56.329 --> 00:15:05.789
You would shoot through your top like...
Have the courage to ask for reality.

00:15:05.789 --> 00:15:08.849
Have that courage! You
are big enough for this.

00:15:08.919 --> 00:15:13.419
In all dimensions of that word.

00:15:17.768 --> 00:15:22.808
We are no small people, even if we look
completely screwed up, we are big people.

00:15:22.802 --> 00:15:25.302
or else She would not
have picked us up,

00:17:36.320 --> 00:17:38.820
The fourth point of the check list

00:19:10.855 --> 00:19:13.355
Fourth is confidence.

00:19:15.185 --> 00:19:19.718
Everybody has difficulties and
everybody has to overcome them.

00:19:19.718 --> 00:19:28.453
Each test is a blessing and each blessing is a test.

00:19:28.454 --> 00:19:34.162
So even if we are not so good in Sahaja
Yoga, even if we don't meditate so well,

00:19:34.187 --> 00:19:40.582
even if we think that our attention is useless, even
if we have within our brains things which are dirty,

00:19:40.574 --> 00:19:43.074
It does not matter,

00:19:44.261 --> 00:19:52.038
because we will overcome. We will
be stronger than negativity.

00:19:52.050 --> 00:19:58.190
We participate in this cosmic
fight against the assuric vidya,

00:19:58.193 --> 00:20:06.297
against the black knowledge of the
evil which is completely active now,

00:20:06.306 --> 00:20:08.116
because the powers
which are given to us

00:20:08.147 --> 00:20:12.806
are greater than the powers
of evil. It is a fact.

00:20:16.206 --> 00:20:18.706
Jai Shri Mataji.

