or she behaves like an aggressive woman,
because the part that is respectable,

00:46:23.889 --> 00:46:28.005
and that is the one which was for
her ascent and was her innate,

00:46:28.005 --> 00:46:31.319
was not at all understood or respected.

00:46:59.853 --> 00:47:07.483
So, the instrument of the left side which are the women of this country were first harmed

00:47:16.376 --> 00:47:22.943
and these became the main
source of troubles in France.

00:47:31.448 --> 00:47:35.011
On the other side, they
became extremely aggressive;

00:47:37.781 --> 00:47:44.133
the men became aggressive and because women were not respected, they also became aggressive.

00:47:48.638 --> 00:47:53.653
The other women who could not
do that became extreme left,

00:47:53.658 --> 00:47:57.988
started crying, weeping and melancholy;

00:47:59.242 --> 00:48:03.720
melancholy character they
developed, melancholy.

00:48:20.165 --> 00:48:26.265
Then they started, you see, writing
about all this melancholy nonsense,

00:48:26.273 --> 00:48:33.275
which doesn’t exist and indulging into
it, like wine or some sort of a thing.

00:48:37.235 --> 00:48:42.502
The movement on the left-hand side, naturally, because men also got attracted towards it,

00:48:42.481 --> 00:48:46.328
made them take to
left-sided food as well.

00:48:52.817 --> 00:49:00.184
Now, for example, they developed the
cheese which was all full of fungus,

00:49:00.224 --> 00:49:03.070
which was dead matter.

00:49:14.020 --> 00:49:16.520
Fungus kills all that is right side;

00:49:20.242 --> 00:49:22.742
anything living can be
killed with fungus.

00:49:26.432 --> 00:49:30.132
Not only as far as the food is
concerned but temperamentally

00:49:30.122 --> 00:49:33.502
gradually they started
becoming like funguses.

00:49:44.777 --> 00:49:52.546
So, the fungus itself has a quality, is
to, that it thrives on the dead matter.

00:49:59.666 --> 00:50:06.579
So they went down to all places where they
could find the dead matter, like Egypt.

00:50:17.015 --> 00:50:20.668
They were not very much interested
in India, even to rule India,

00:50:26.082 --> 00:50:32.849
but they were very much interested
in Egyptian dead things

00:50:32.860 --> 00:50:39.011
and other places wherever they could
find this dead stuff available to them.

00:50:51.399 --> 00:50:57.270
Also, I would say Christianity,
which started decaying very much,

00:50:57.302 --> 00:50:59.802
became a big hold in France.

00:51:14.438 --> 00:51:17.192
Religion also became like a fungus;

00:51:26.160 --> 00:51:35.380
like building, say, big churches
and around them to bury the dead.

00:51:44.518 --> 00:51:51.183
Now, I went to see Chartres; you have a
beautiful, a very, very beautiful church

00:51:51.217 --> 00:51:58.743
and very good work done by the artist, but there are lying all dead bodies all around, it’s horrible.

00:52:11.363 --> 00:52:18.248
Actually, dead people should be burnt,
only the realised soul can be buried.

00:52:37.684 --> 00:52:47.099
The sense of respect was lacking very much,
even in the history, you can see clearly.

00:52:52.855 --> 00:52:55.355
What was important
throughout was the money.

00:52:59.775 --> 00:53:08.522
As I see the French revolution took place when I must say the queen was not a bad woman at all.

00:53:22.203 --> 00:53:26.248
She was actually a great protégée.

00:53:26.254 --> 00:53:31.218
She was a protector of all the artists of France

00:53:31.204 --> 00:53:37.923
and she’s the one who gave such a
great momentum to the art of France.

00:53:46.923 --> 00:53:55.720
If she created something like a furniture piece or any building, today even you show it with pride.

00:54:00.512 --> 00:54:06.858
After all she was not going to take it with
her; it was for France she made everything.

00:54:10.611 --> 00:54:13.764
But the French wanted more
money to be distributed.

00:54:13.764 --> 00:54:17.881
For what? For drinking more wine,

00:54:27.499 --> 00:54:30.551
not to create anything
of eternal interest.

00:54:39.711 --> 00:54:44.466
That’s why I say those who drink have no
right to strike, or to ask for more money

00:54:44.445 --> 00:54:48.247
because they have more money,
that’s why they drink.

00:55:02.192 --> 00:55:09.040
So, I don’t believe in capitalism, but I do believe that those who can create something new,

00:55:09.040 --> 00:55:17.031
who can create something – not new in the sense of nonsense, but a thing of eternal values

00:55:17.053 --> 00:55:20.731
must be given money to create that.

00:55:36.057 --> 00:55:38.557
There are many capitalists
who do wrong things,

00:55:38.557 --> 00:55:43.992
like buying instruments of
war and things like that.

00:55:53.832 --> 00:55:56.953
Now we have England, we have America,

00:55:56.953 --> 00:56:01.551
they’re doing this and creating
concrete jungle for the progeny.

00:56:03.686 --> 00:56:06.556
Great Britain and England
and America is doing this.

00:56:06.561 --> 00:56:11.623
is to buy more weapons and otherwise
creating concrete jungles.

00:56:22.981 --> 00:56:30.265
And in Russia they say that they are giving equal distribution, but people drink like fish.

00:56:47.090 --> 00:56:49.405
So, with this French revolution also,

00:56:49.403 --> 00:56:56.575
the drinking became a part and
parcel of the lives of the French,

00:56:56.575 --> 00:56:59.075
because they got easy money.

00:57:17.058 --> 00:57:23.998
So, the more money was acquired for
doing all kinds of unrighteous things,

00:57:24.020 --> 00:57:29.044
unholy things and, we can
say, inauspicious things.

00:57:37.354 --> 00:57:41.600
But there were poor people, perhaps
they did not drink so much,

00:57:41.617 --> 00:57:45.610
who created great architecture
here in this country.

00:57:54.907 --> 00:58:00.553
Despite that, great artists were born
in this country who had no money.

00:58:00.562 --> 00:58:06.124
They died, becoming mad
or becoming paupers.

00:58:22.234 --> 00:58:29.284
Now we have Napoleon, another person
who tried to conquer other places;

00:58:29.314 --> 00:58:33.321
he’s another ego trip that
he did in the history.

00:58:39.871 --> 00:58:42.591
But still he was not
a very ignoble person

00:58:42.591 --> 00:58:47.650
as we find so many of them are
these days, who are the rulers.

00:58:54.908 --> 00:59:00.440
The only thing I feel about him that
he didn’t have a great character

00:59:00.438 --> 00:59:04.040
to leave any great
impress on people,

00:59:04.040 --> 00:59:08.878
how to enhance their
life in their quality.

00:59:29.315 --> 00:59:35.947
So, the people who could have really
impressed your minds towards the ascent

00:59:35.974 --> 00:59:40.157
were all paupers or became
mad or were wasted.

01:00:03.612 --> 01:00:16.271
Ultimately, I think the whole aggressiveness disappeared
with understanding that it is no use aggressing,

01:00:16.247 --> 01:00:20.771
but the left movement still
remained very prevalent.

01:00:37.635 --> 01:00:44.951
So, for the rest of the world, French
are very weird, queer, strange people.

01:00:51.620 --> 01:00:56.518
They developed their own insular
methods of dealing with things.

01:01:03.298 --> 01:01:10.924
This is, I would say, is a curse because that kind of a curse when it works out, then you cannot improve

01:01:10.924 --> 01:01:16.257
as you have nothing else to
see and relate and to advance.

01:01:28.792 --> 01:01:37.160
Because the ego when it is worked with the left problems, you can be very queer, strange and weird.

01:01:44.256 --> 01:01:49.502
I could see that the
first day I came to Paris,

01:01:53.826 --> 01:01:59.216
and they told Me very clearly
that, “Mother, don’t smile at all,

01:02:06.922 --> 01:02:09.422
and You have to keep very serious.”

01:02:10.874 --> 01:02:15.991
And I cannot be serious for more than
two minutes, I think, two minutes.

01:02:21.528 --> 01:02:24.630
So, I said, “But why?”

01:02:24.647 --> 01:02:28.463
The reason, they said was that, “They
will think that You are an ignoramus,

01:02:28.453 --> 01:02:30.313
You don’t know what’s
happening in this world:

01:02:30.341 --> 01:02:34.083
serious things are happening
and You are laughing.

01:02:41.129 --> 01:02:44.374
So, they will think that
You are not at all matured.”

01:02:49.754 --> 01:02:56.517
But as soon as I started My lecture, I
looked at those people who were so serious

01:03:05.228 --> 01:03:08.756
and I couldn’t control My laughter!

01:03:16.981 --> 01:03:19.481
I hope it is changing.

01:03:23.498 --> 01:03:26.668
And then I said,

01:03:26.677 --> 01:03:32.248
“Sorry, I’m addressing all the les
Misérables which I have heard about."

01:03:40.462 --> 01:03:46.860
I am so happy to see today, that
veil of gloom, has passed over.

01:03:58.362 --> 01:04:02.222
As if lot of dirty mud
had gathered over here

01:04:02.207 --> 01:04:06.077
and the lotuses were
about to bloom out,

01:04:16.252 --> 01:04:19.523
whatever may be the atmosphere,
whatever may be the history,

01:04:19.539 --> 01:04:24.458
whatever may be that has been
created by human beings,

01:04:24.447 --> 01:04:33.812
inside resides beautiful lotus
petals, everything intact.

01:04:46.542 --> 01:04:51.097
With a little push they are
all out now in the atmosphere

01:04:51.123 --> 01:04:56.747
spreading their fragrance in this
dirty pool what we call as France.

01:05:12.037 --> 01:05:20.987
And they’re such strong people, very strong Sahaja Yogis in France which really makes Me very happy and proud.

01:05:32.709 --> 01:05:36.632
In the beginning I used to come
every third week to Paris

01:05:36.638 --> 01:05:42.532
and have a meeting and when they asked,
“Mother, why are You so much visiting Paris?”

01:05:42.551 --> 01:05:45.051
I said, “That is the gate of the hell.”

01:05:54.332 --> 01:06:01.082
You must have heard the story I’ve told
you about the advertising department.

01:06:07.326 --> 01:06:11.096
Ok I had better tell them.

01:06:11.090 --> 01:06:16.480
You see, two men who had done lot
of good as Sahaja Yogis maybe,

01:06:16.460 --> 01:06:20.310
when they died, they were
asked to go to Heaven.

01:06:27.862 --> 01:06:31.772
So they went to Heaven and there they
found everybody was meditating,

01:06:31.772 --> 01:06:36.791
so they said, “What is new about this,
we were meditating in the world?”

01:06:44.319 --> 01:06:50.039
So they said, “Why not we..."
They asked the permission of God,

01:06:50.039 --> 01:06:52.931
that, "Can we see also
Hell, if we have a chance?

01:06:52.930 --> 01:06:55.600
Because we... then we
can decide you see,

01:06:55.611 --> 01:06:58.478
whether we want to be here or there."

01:07:08.348 --> 01:07:10.848
You see that is what the ego
is, you must have choice.

01:07:16.817 --> 01:07:19.777
So they went to Hell,

01:07:22.290 --> 01:07:28.457
and when they entered the first big hall, they found all kind of music was going on,

01:07:28.497 --> 01:07:34.767
funny type of music and you know like Halloween you have all kinds of dirty things

01:07:34.797 --> 01:07:37.297
and women were dancing nude,

01:07:37.297 --> 01:07:38.987
and the men were singing nude

01:07:39.007 --> 01:07:42.377
and they were doing all funny, funny
things there, which we call funny.

01:08:02.617 --> 01:08:08.385
So, they said, “This seems to
be better place for a change,”

01:08:14.531 --> 01:08:18.371
because drinking was free,
everything was free there;

01:08:20.585 --> 01:08:23.085
drugs,

01:08:26.293 --> 01:08:28.793
all nice, nice things there!

01:08:34.624 --> 01:08:37.774
So, they said, “It's
very nice place.”

01:08:37.798 --> 01:08:40.888
So, the people who were in charge
said, “What are you doing here?”

01:08:48.638 --> 01:08:52.882
So they said, “We’ve come to visit
the Hell, where is the Hell?”

01:09:00.161 --> 01:09:03.741
So, they said, “You can see from this
hole”, and they took them to a hole

01:09:03.762 --> 01:09:06.262
from where they could
see the picture of Hell.

01:09:12.233 --> 01:09:15.829
And there they found people
hanging on top of fire,

01:09:15.832 --> 01:09:23.227
or they were put in the boiling oil
and they were put in the dirty mud;

01:09:23.229 --> 01:09:26.172
all kinds of things, you see,
and they were horrified.

01:09:37.751 --> 01:09:40.161
And some were whipped very
badly, and I don’t know,

01:09:40.161 --> 01:09:43.201
all kinds of punishments
that are possible.

01:09:46.469 --> 01:09:47.999
So, they got a fright and they said,

01:09:48.028 --> 01:09:51.068
“Now if that is Hell, what
is this in this hall?”

01:09:55.973 --> 01:10:00.591
They said, “This is the
Advertising Department of Hell.”

01:10:24.744 --> 01:10:29.628
And the ideas were coming from
French and English specialists,

01:10:29.646 --> 01:10:33.592
and other specialists from
other European countries also.

01:10:42.065 --> 01:10:44.922
And nowadays the Swiss must be
doing all the banking there.

01:10:53.396 --> 01:10:58.909
So that is the advertising
department about which,

01:10:58.909 --> 01:11:02.879
you see, one should be quite knowledgeable,

01:11:02.878 --> 01:11:05.879
to know what is the advertising
department of Hell is.

01:11:14.673 --> 01:11:19.213
So, the righteousness and the holiness

01:11:19.247 --> 01:11:27.537
can only be maintained if you are very
careful about this advertising departments,

01:11:27.536 --> 01:11:30.782
especially in France and other countries.

01:11:43.847 --> 01:11:50.744
The left side works in this way
that we want to destroy ourselves,

01:11:54.342 --> 01:11:59.974
because left side stands for
desire as well as for destruction.

01:12:03.616 --> 01:12:09.963
It can destroy all if there
is no desire of God anymore.

01:12:13.895 --> 01:12:20.625
So, when you start getting to
the other side of your desires,

01:12:20.609 --> 01:12:23.945
you have a desire to destroy yourself.

01:12:32.249 --> 01:12:45.092
Yesterday only I read in a newspaper
an English lady who left millions of pounds,
killed herself by malnutrition.

01:12:55.308 --> 01:13:03.575
So, this idea of destroying yourself is now justifying so many things that we do in this world,

01:13:03.572 --> 01:13:06.212
which should not be done for our health,

01:13:06.214 --> 01:13:10.212
for our physical, mental and
emotional and spiritual health.

01:13:23.979 --> 01:13:30.455
And this tendency is to be seen by
Sahaja Yogis within themselves also.

01:13:36.960 --> 01:13:40.060
When the Sahaja Yogis start slipping out

01:13:40.070 --> 01:13:43.230
and you tell them, "You are slipping
out, now don't go that way."

01:13:43.247 --> 01:13:47.687
so they say, “No, leave me alone,
it’s all right, I can manage myself,”

01:13:47.697 --> 01:13:50.197
means, “I can destroy myself.”

01:14:03.038 --> 01:14:16.378
And this anti-life behaviour starts to such an extent, that they denied all that was spiritual, all that was healthy.

01:14:27.599 --> 01:14:32.299
Also on the left-hand side you had
some horrible writers and authors,

01:14:32.319 --> 01:14:33.779
who came on this earth

01:14:33.786 --> 01:14:38.400
to give you very, very,
very, very anti-life ideas;

01:14:49.072 --> 01:14:53.701
like a person like Sade, you see,
who started sadism and all that,

01:14:53.721 --> 01:14:56.231
this kind of people only
could prosper in France

01:14:56.261 --> 01:14:58.902
in India such a person
would have been thrown out.

01:15:05.001 --> 01:15:10.226
Some mad fellow might have written “Kama
Sutra” but I’ve never known that book,

01:15:10.227 --> 01:15:12.918
I’ve never read that book, I
don’t know anything about it

01:15:12.943 --> 01:15:16.478
and I don’t know if you ask anyone they’ll
say, “What is that book? We don’t know.”

01:15:31.693 --> 01:15:35.951
But if you say “Gita”, if you say “Ramayana”
you’ll find many or most of them.

01:15:42.778 --> 01:15:46.572
Even the Christians in India
won’t read such a book.

01:15:53.838 --> 01:15:58.092
Now, but these books were
very much appreciated.

01:15:58.083 --> 01:16:04.862
You find, it’s hard to find, anyone in Europe who’s educated and who has not read these books.

01:16:04.876 --> 01:16:07.376
It's like a Bible for them.

01:16:16.731 --> 01:16:22.377
I mean, all these things have made
them immune to sin, the filth of sin.

01:16:34.545 --> 01:16:37.255
To add to problems,
you had so many wars,

01:16:37.255 --> 01:16:41.485
but last war, France was occupied
by these horrible Germans.

01:16:49.434 --> 01:16:51.934
So, they were in complete fear,

01:16:56.178 --> 01:16:59.692
again another left-sided movement.

01:17:04.758 --> 01:17:11.896
All these things have added to the
perpetuation of left sided problems.

01:17:18.099 --> 01:17:21.746
Now how to get rid of them is our problem.

01:17:25.096 --> 01:17:32.556
When I came here, Patrick told Me how they found people possessed by all kinds of variety of bhoots,

01:17:45.724 --> 01:17:50.846
and I’m not surprised because I was
expecting it sometimes to happen.

01:17:55.970 --> 01:18:01.070
There are still many Sahaja Yogis,
especially Yoginis, who are possessed.

01:18:08.441 --> 01:18:13.350
I know of one mad one who came to My
house, broke all the house and everything

01:18:13.369 --> 01:18:19.240
and did lot of things,
French, you know, a man.

01:18:36.703 --> 01:18:42.222
So, to get out of it, first of all
we must know the dangers of it.

01:18:45.041 --> 01:18:52.112
If the women go on like this, don’t obey
their leaders and go on with it, saying
that,  “This is my right”

01:18:52.083 --> 01:18:57.717
Don’t meditate and do all kinds of
things, they’ll become schizophrenic.

01:19:17.631 --> 01:19:22.211
The schizophrenia, according to
Me, according to Sahaja Yoga,

01:19:22.212 --> 01:19:30.252
is a disease in which you are permanently
possessed by many of these dead spirits,

01:19:42.657 --> 01:19:47.417
and in India they would be
sent to lunatic asylums.

01:19:50.925 --> 01:19:58.559
But I’m told that they have now cancelled
all lunatic asylums everywhere and the
lunatics are moving on the streets.

01:20:07.590 --> 01:20:10.090
It’s a very serious situation.

01:20:12.829 --> 01:20:17.224
The government doesn’t
realise what they’re doing.

01:20:23.859 --> 01:20:32.497
Once I travelled by bus in Paris and I saw one after another, people, one lady, then one gentleman

01:20:32.507 --> 01:20:38.099
then one other gentleman, they walked in, and they were talking to themselves loudly.

01:20:49.597 --> 01:20:53.428
They’re all possessed people
and they’ll possess you.

01:21:01.335 --> 01:21:06.781
They will possess you, they will possess your children, they can possess your pets, anyone.

01:21:12.170 --> 01:21:16.573
Such abnormal people should
be kept away from the public.

01:21:21.189 --> 01:21:27.639
But Marie told Me that, “You see, these French are very sympathetic towards them.”

01:21:33.068 --> 01:21:42.067
Their bhoots are also, I must tell you, the left sided people, they try to do things to incur your sympathies.

01:21:51.959 --> 01:21:58.454
In the right-sided people, as they are
aggressive to attract your attention,

01:21:58.468 --> 01:22:04.084
the left-sided people are aggressive to
themselves to attract your attention.

01:22:19.486 --> 01:22:29.476
So those people who think, “We can wear some scanty clothes in winter time, or we can torture our lives, stand on our heads,”

01:22:29.445 --> 01:22:38.532
all such people are  absolutely now passing
the limits of advertising department.

01:22:50.452 --> 01:22:57.910
So, the first things Sahaja Yogis have to remember that you have come on this earth to enjoy.

01:23:08.510 --> 01:23:09.030
Enjoy.

01:23:09.040 --> 01:23:09.870
In French!

01:23:09.870 --> 01:23:11.230
No, no French!

01:23:13.267 --> 01:23:15.767
Difficult Shri Mataji.

01:23:30.105 --> 01:23:37.235
Imagine, they said there is no word in French for enjoyment as I heard today, but for fun.

01:23:37.255 --> 01:23:38.215
Fun!

01:23:38.203 --> 01:23:40.263
Fun, they've found one, Shri Mataji.

01:23:40.278 --> 01:23:43.233
Found, Thank God!

01:23:43.248 --> 01:23:48.382
So, this is fun, you have
to enjoy the fun of life,

01:23:53.066 --> 01:23:57.292
and you are not here
to suffer any more.

01:23:57.302 --> 01:23:59.592
you’re not to suffer anymore.

01:24:02.803 --> 01:24:06.352
And to be serious – for what?

01:24:15.082 --> 01:24:23.870
And to be tense is out of, out of absolutely we can say, is out of subject, is useless to be tense.

01:24:23.879 --> 01:24:28.360
How can you be tense in the
atmosphere which is so relaxed?

01:24:33.924 --> 01:24:41.874
If these things are expressing themselves, then you should know you haven’t come to your proper point in Sahaja Yoga.

01:24:48.675 --> 01:24:55.015
If you still worry and go on worrying, you’ll go to the left and you’ll get out of Sahaja Yoga.

01:24:55.015 --> 01:24:57.515
This is the second serious point.

01:25:07.580 --> 01:25:14.340
So, the first point is that you’ll
become schizophrenic, mad, lunatics.

01:25:17.730 --> 01:25:18.768
That’s the first thing,

01:25:18.768 --> 01:25:21.268
I’m not a businessman so I’m
telling you the worst first.

01:25:38.818 --> 01:25:45.201
The second thing as just now I’ve told you will be that you’ll go out of Sahaja Yoga.

01:25:57.591 --> 01:26:03.695
As a result of that, you might
get any disease like cancer

01:26:08.307 --> 01:26:14.167
or any disease that comes from
the left side, there are so many.

01:26:19.415 --> 01:26:26.545
So, this is very important to see that you
try to keep to the central path of ascent,

01:26:35.288 --> 01:26:44.758
through curative methods, through meditative methods, through vibratory methods you must try to keep in the centre and don’t go to the right.

01:26:55.400 --> 01:26:58.710
Because with this destructive power,

01:26:58.692 --> 01:27:02.330
with this destructive power,
if you go to the right side,

01:27:02.330 --> 01:27:04.110
you will become extremely inauspicious

01:27:04.120 --> 01:27:06.620
and you’ll start destroying people,

01:27:12.839 --> 01:27:17.992
especially for the wives of leaders, I would like to tell them that they must become very humble,

01:27:18.004 --> 01:27:24.022
otherwise they will have this thing, a power by which they’ll destroy themselves and others.

01:27:34.989 --> 01:27:38.467
This is like this the power,
say, which is of a fire

01:27:38.444 --> 01:27:43.597
or of the light, if it is not
used for which it is made,

01:27:43.593 --> 01:27:50.046
supposing you put your hand
in the fire, it will burn,

01:28:01.886 --> 01:28:09.010
So, we must understand the power of
women is compassion, is nourishment,

01:28:15.053 --> 01:28:21.435
and they should not try to become like men, because then they’ll burn off people and burn off themselves.

01:28:31.532 --> 01:28:41.212
So, as I’ve told you before that it’s the women who can be very, very helpful in improving the left side.

01:28:47.376 --> 01:28:53.790
By dominating men, you make them left-sided which is not their style. They should not be left sided.

01:29:06.170 --> 01:29:11.019
But if they are truly men, they
will walk in the central path;

01:29:17.724 --> 01:29:22.724
and if women are truly women,
they’ll walk in the central path.

01:29:25.884 --> 01:29:28.484
So to walk in the central path

01:29:28.484 --> 01:29:30.984
one has to get rid of all these
things, of this type are within us.

01:29:44.760 --> 01:29:48.790
The third thing that really,
I would say, warn you people,

01:29:48.770 --> 01:29:52.320
that you get attached to your things

01:29:52.324 --> 01:29:56.156
to your possessions,

01:30:04.595 --> 01:30:06.536
to your children,

01:30:07.901 --> 01:30:11.121
to your surroundings:

01:30:12.673 --> 01:30:17.291
like many French would say, “Oh,
I hate to go out of France.”

01:30:22.192 --> 01:30:26.053
When they go to some other
country they always criticise.

01:30:30.603 --> 01:30:35.163
I don’t know who are the best critics,
but all of them criticise each other;

01:30:37.629 --> 01:30:41.673
they never try to see the good points of others;

01:30:43.864 --> 01:30:49.517
and in doing so, what you do is to
perpetuate a kind of an inferiority on others

01:30:49.511 --> 01:30:56.981
using your powers of left side by
which you make others look small.

01:31:00.783 --> 01:31:04.523
Like pitying someone for nothing at all;

01:31:04.523 --> 01:31:08.013
like if supposing you start
pitying Me, what will it look like?

01:31:12.153 --> 01:31:14.533
It’s absurd as that!

01:31:14.553 --> 01:31:17.053
Yes Shri Mataji. I don’t even
know how to translate that.

01:31:17.071 --> 01:31:19.571
I know, but that’s what it is.

01:31:44.929 --> 01:31:47.429
So there should be no pity,
there should be compassion,

01:31:50.197 --> 01:31:55.627
and that will take you out of this
nonsensical idea of pitying yourself,

01:31:55.627 --> 01:32:01.387
pitying others and feeling all
the time sorry for nothing at all;

01:32:06.345 --> 01:32:11.155
because if you ask for such
pity then you’ll be pitied too.

01:32:11.168 --> 01:32:13.668
I mean, you’ll be in a
pitiable condition yourself.

01:32:23.760 --> 01:32:28.469
But if you have compassion, then
you don’t put down that person,

01:32:28.469 --> 01:32:31.999
you don’t sort of make him feel inferior

01:32:32.029 --> 01:32:35.769
but you encourage him
and he feels powerful.

01:32:43.410 --> 01:32:45.180
Like a finger is hurt within you,

01:32:45.180 --> 01:32:49.830
you just try to soothe it and
be compassionate towards it.

01:32:49.822 --> 01:32:52.402
You don’t try to put him
down that “You’re no good,

01:32:52.403 --> 01:32:54.903
because he's part and
parcel of your being.

01:33:09.976 --> 01:33:14.423
So, the compassion stands in
between condemnation and pity.

01:33:22.509 --> 01:33:27.331
In compassion you have to
condemn whatever is wrong.

01:33:31.941 --> 01:33:36.553
You have to condemn the bhoots. You
have to condemn that’s ugliness’s.

01:33:38.471 --> 01:33:40.971
You have to condemn
all that is wrong.

01:33:43.454 --> 01:33:47.974
So, by that, you see,
you make that person see

01:33:47.964 --> 01:33:51.224
that you do not have appreciation

01:33:51.232 --> 01:33:56.767
of what he is at all and it is just
compassion and no pity about it;

01:34:07.902 --> 01:34:13.389
because the left-sided people want to be pitied and if you pity them, they get even worse.

01:34:24.237 --> 01:34:33.047
So, to say, “Poor person, poor man”, or
a “Poor old lady - something” is wrong.

01:34:41.370 --> 01:34:47.980
So when the people who are possessed
they start condemning their bhoots,

01:34:47.980 --> 01:34:49.935
they come up.

01:35:00.465 --> 01:35:05.924
When they hate their bhoots, they
can get rid of them in no time.

01:35:18.050 --> 01:35:22.577
But sometimes going worse than
that, they get identified.

01:35:29.051 --> 01:35:32.011
Of course to judge it, best
is to see through vibrations

01:35:32.001 --> 01:35:35.001
but you can also see it logically,

01:35:35.001 --> 01:35:40.391
how we behave towards our
possessions, towards others.

01:35:50.655 --> 01:35:54.915
Lot of work has been done in India
on a very subtle level, I would say,

01:35:54.935 --> 01:35:57.795
how to get out of the left side.

01:36:02.937 --> 01:36:07.467
I would say Mahavira was the one
who really has worked very hard

01:36:07.467 --> 01:36:13.807
to give the whole idea of the hell up
to heaven, what the left side is.

01:36:16.202 --> 01:36:19.992
Another, I would say, his own
incarnation, was William Blake,

01:36:19.992 --> 01:36:22.492
who has also given full idea about it.

01:36:25.337 --> 01:36:27.837
I would say Dante did the same.

01:36:30.612 --> 01:36:33.286
So, this is what they have shown you,

01:36:33.286 --> 01:36:36.826
how the hell is and
how the heavens are.

01:36:40.651 --> 01:36:45.252
Now for Sahaja Yogis, it is important
to see their left-sided problems

01:36:45.244 --> 01:36:47.744
if they are lingering in them.

01:36:51.324 --> 01:36:54.702
Possession means you’re
possessed by something,

01:36:54.683 --> 01:37:00.302
some ideas which are not
rational, which are illogical.

01:37:06.005 --> 01:37:10.333
And in the modern times, I’ve seen how
they avoid the topic if you ask them,

01:37:10.345 --> 01:37:13.143
they say, “I don’t know.”

01:37:18.871 --> 01:37:21.371
“I don’t know why I feel like
that,” then give up that feeling,

01:37:21.371 --> 01:37:23.871
it’s wrong; if you don’t
know, it’s no good.

01:37:29.683 --> 01:37:34.373
In the beginning you asked French, any French, “How are you?” they would say, like this.

01:37:34.386 --> 01:37:39.393
And I would look at their
hands, what does that mean?

01:37:48.226 --> 01:37:50.726
No, like this.

01:37:52.947 --> 01:37:57.435
So, I used to wonder, what’s
wrong with the hand!

01:38:08.458 --> 01:38:13.019
And they were very boastful about
it that’s the best part of it;

01:38:13.003 --> 01:38:15.968
because to say something as certain, cocksure,

01:38:15.976 --> 01:38:18.328
was regarded as ego for them perhaps,

01:38:18.324 --> 01:38:21.965
but Sahaja Yogis have to be cocksure.

01:38:29.014 --> 01:38:34.226
Now, English, if I ask them, “How are
you?” they would say, “Confused.”

01:38:40.872 --> 01:38:45.592
So, I mean, I didn’t know why,
and boastingly, “I’m confused,”

01:38:45.592 --> 01:38:48.092
as something great, you
know that “I’m confused.”

01:38:52.499 --> 01:38:57.230
So, the explanation was given, was
that, that we are aware of our state,

01:38:57.245 --> 01:39:00.290
we are not saying something
with a cocksure way.

01:39:09.683 --> 01:39:13.286
A Sahaja Yogi, if he is confused,
he is not a Sahaja Yogi.

01:39:19.423 --> 01:39:25.290
At this stage you have to be
absolutely sure of yourself,

01:39:28.587 --> 01:39:35.270
sure about Me, sure about Sahaja Yoga and sure about all the Sahaja Yogis of the world.

01:39:40.132 --> 01:39:42.632
Otherwise you’re not Sahaja Yogis.

01:39:46.080 --> 01:39:56.993
That means your connection with God
is like a loose plug, like that.

01:40:04.827 --> 01:40:09.757
So, we have to understand that
in the centre when we are,

01:40:09.736 --> 01:40:14.027
we are sure of what we
are, absolutely sure.

01:40:18.195 --> 01:40:20.695
We raise our heads
in pride and glory.

01:40:26.376 --> 01:40:30.516
We don’t have the vanity of the
right and the pity of the left.

01:40:35.842 --> 01:40:41.105
That’s what is we are going
to achieve in France now.

01:40:44.959 --> 01:40:49.085
No more going to the sub-conscious
or to the collective sub-conscious.

01:40:53.131 --> 01:40:55.909
Now don’t think of your
forefathers what they did,

01:40:58.122 --> 01:41:02.515
nor think of the future, what
your progeny’s going to do.

01:41:07.608 --> 01:41:11.150
Think for yourself what you’re
going to do for both of them.

01:41:15.421 --> 01:41:22.327
Many cursed families can be completely
redeemed by one good Sahaja Yogi;

01:41:29.815 --> 01:41:35.183
and thousands of years of progeny
can be blessed by one Sahaja Yogi.

01:41:47.376 --> 01:41:52.001
That’s a fact, you can
feel the vibrations now.

01:41:54.492 --> 01:41:57.062
So, one should have that personality

01:41:57.062 --> 01:42:02.432
of a very tranquil, peaceful, understanding,

01:42:09.364 --> 01:42:15.155
but this understanding should not be
mental but a sap on your central path,

01:42:21.993 --> 01:42:29.235
the vital energy that nourishes all the
chakras, your being and the atmosphere.

01:42:34.849 --> 01:42:38.689
I’m sure all the French
Sahaja Yogis now

01:42:38.689 --> 01:42:42.459
will take to the new ways
of the central path.

01:42:51.658 --> 01:42:56.332
They should wear
dresses which are fresh,

01:42:56.346 --> 01:43:04.406
have fresh looks on their faces, should
create a fresh atmosphere around.

01:43:09.640 --> 01:43:13.577
Give up all worn-out things that,
they’re very fond of worn-out things,

01:43:13.577 --> 01:43:17.717
and also worn-out houses they
like, they say it is antique.

01:43:21.749 --> 01:43:25.396
Worn out clothes
and worn out houses!

01:43:36.749 --> 01:43:41.879
No, no give up that idea of antiques also

01:43:41.861 --> 01:43:45.419
because, you see antiques
are not all right

01:43:45.402 --> 01:43:47.902
as long as they are
preserved properly,

01:43:47.902 --> 01:43:54.237
but if you make them look like antiques,
you see, it's no respect given to them.

01:44:08.539 --> 01:44:14.149
I went to Poland and I was surprised
that all their old monuments

01:44:14.149 --> 01:44:16.649
were resurrected after the war

01:44:16.637 --> 01:44:21.544
and everything is painted and
brought back to absolute fresh look.

01:44:28.284 --> 01:44:34.752
They haven’t kept anything broken
or muddy or in any way worn-out.

01:44:49.434 --> 01:44:53.558
So, the idea of this antiques to
be preserved as they are

01:44:53.563 --> 01:44:57.584
is also, I think, very bhootish and left-sided.

01:45:04.985 --> 01:45:08.955
So, your antiques whatever you may
possess also must be cleaned out

01:45:08.942 --> 01:45:10.645
and properly done up

01:45:10.650 --> 01:45:14.098
and should be brought to a fresh look.

01:45:29.501 --> 01:45:32.939
Now this necklace I’m wearing
is very antique, very old,

01:45:32.937 --> 01:45:35.437
but doesn’t look old, does it?

01:45:40.845 --> 01:45:44.276
Because it is looked after and it would look funny

01:45:44.276 --> 01:45:51.607
to wear, for a Goddess, to wear a
antique thing which looks so worn out.

01:46:08.209 --> 01:46:14.528
So, one criteria could be that whatever
we wear or do, will Mother like it?

01:46:22.477 --> 01:46:24.069
This is the one question you can ask

01:46:24.072 --> 01:46:30.172
if you don’t want to ask the vibrations,
“Will She like it? We have to please Her.”

01:46:35.243 --> 01:46:38.223
And I tell you: very small,
small things please Me.

01:46:41.329 --> 01:46:46.772
You don’t have to do too many things,
just a few things which pleases Me,

01:46:46.772 --> 01:46:49.272
which are very simple and easy and innate

01:46:58.817 --> 01:47:01.317
Like you have to be innocent.

01:47:02.508 --> 01:47:06.452
It’s very easy if you are a child-like person,

01:47:06.452 --> 01:47:09.592
you just don’t allow any
cunning to come into your head,

01:47:09.577 --> 01:47:12.689
any absurd ideas, just be innocent;

01:47:12.693 --> 01:47:16.263
you don’t have to do
anything to be innocent.

01:47:23.366 --> 01:47:25.866
You have to do something
to be non-innocent.

01:47:30.988 --> 01:47:33.218
So, this is what one has to understand

01:47:33.238 --> 01:47:37.778
that the basis of our
left side is innocence.

01:47:42.747 --> 01:47:45.247
So, anything that is not
innocent, we should not do.

01:47:49.376 --> 01:47:51.474
It's so simple.

01:47:52.823 --> 01:47:57.033
should be all right with all of us

01:47:57.033 --> 01:48:04.133
if we just believe that we have this quality
of innocence within us absolutely intact,

01:48:11.003 --> 01:48:15.304
and you have to just awaken
it and enjoy it, that's all.

01:48:21.613 --> 01:48:23.804
So may God bless you all,

01:48:23.804 --> 01:48:27.744
may God give you
strength to be innocent.

01:48:36.084 --> 01:48:40.029
You must pray that
you should be innocent

01:48:46.318 --> 01:48:49.908
and the innocence will
suck in all your problems,

01:48:49.908 --> 01:48:52.408
suck in your the problems of the left side,

01:48:58.443 --> 01:49:04.291
and the symbol of innocence is Shri Ganesh,
who just knows His Mother, nobody else

01:49:11.795 --> 01:49:15.369
and His innocence is the
source of all the wisdom.

01:49:17.982 --> 01:49:23.935
So, you have to pray for becoming
absolutely innocent people.

01:49:27.070 --> 01:49:29.570
May God bless you.

01:49:34.226 --> 01:49:40.696
Shri Mataji, if I may draw Your
attention on this decoration.

01:49:40.702 --> 01:49:46.188
On this crest is the lily who is
the symbol of ancient France,

01:49:46.188 --> 01:49:51.128
who represents the flower of
purity in the French tradition

01:49:51.161 --> 01:49:54.368
and represents the kundalini which
goes through the Agnya Chakra

01:49:54.368 --> 01:49:58.769
with both ego and superego being
pushed and diminished on the side.

01:49:58.779 --> 01:50:02.429
And we pray, Shri Mataji, that that
should be the result of our innocence

01:50:02.448 --> 01:50:06.669
that we should all be beautiful
French lilies for You, Shri Mataji

01:50:06.688 --> 01:50:07.568
Thank you.

